717792f-b.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 193rd Street (West)
717792f-b.text:
Broadway, at west 193rd Street, showing the Sowerby house on the eest side of Broacwey. On the ridge in view 3 is the Tweed Castle (left) anc the C. K. G. Billings stable.
E. P. Chrystie  June, 1923
